---
---

<section id="story" class="py-20 md:py-24 bg-white relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 relative">
    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light text-botanical mb-6">Our Love Story</h2>
      <div class="w-40 h-0.5 bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-sage to-transparent mx-auto mt-8"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-[4/2.75] group">
        <img src="/img/story.jpg" alt="How We Met" loading="lazy" class="relative px-3 w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" />
        <img src="/img/frame2.png" alt="frame" loading="lazy" class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" />
      </div>

      <div class="relative space-y-12">
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-4xl font-light text-botanical mb-4 flex items-center">
            How We Met
            <img src="/img/flower1.png" alt="flower" class="inline-flex ms-2 max-w-8" loading="lazy" />
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            It was a rainy autumn evening in October 2019 at a cozy coffee shop in downtown Portland. Emma was reading her favorite novel when Lucas accidentally spilled his latte. What started as an embarrassing moment turned into hours of conversation and laughter.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-4xl font-light text-botanical mb-4 flex items-center">
            The Proposal
            <img src="/img/flower2.png" alt="flower 2" class="inline-flex ms-2 max-w-8" loading="lazy" />
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Two years later, Lucas planned the perfect surprise. He took Emma back to that same coffee shop where they first met. After a nostalgic walk through their favorite spots, he got down on one knee in the park where they had their first picnic. With the sunset painting the sky in shades of pink and gold, Emma said yes through happy tears.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
